<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Página-1" id="v4w0xNLlb51hintJ34AH">
    <mxGraphModel dx="3828" dy="-4016" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml predict_grpc_onnx\ntitle Predict — gRPC + ONNX Backend\n\nskinparam sequenceMessageAlign center\nskinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true\nskinparam maxMessageSize 200\nskinparam ParticipantPadding 20\nskinparam BoxPadding 10\nskinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5\nskinparam roundcorner 5\nskinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #DAE8FC\nskinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #333333\nskinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA\nskinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC\n\nactor \&quot;Caller\&quot; as Caller\n\nbox \&quot;mlinference::client\&quot; #EAF4FB\n    participant \&quot;InferenceClient\&quot; as IC\n    participant \&quot;GrpcClientBackend\&quot; as GCB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;Network / gRPC\&quot; #F5F5F5\n    participant \&quot;WorkerService::Stub\&quot; as Stub\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;mlinference::worker (server)\&quot; #EAF7EA\n    participant \&quot;WorkerServiceImpl\&quot; as WSI\n    participant \&quot;InferenceEngine\&quot; as IE\n    participant \&quot;OnnxBackend\&quot; as OB\nend box\n\n== Setup (já conectado) ==\n\nCaller -&gt; IC : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate IC\n\nIC -&gt; GCB : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate GCB\n\nnote right of GCB\n  **value_convert.hpp**\n  to_proto_struct(inputs)\n  Object → google::protobuf::Struct\nend note\n\nGCB -&gt; GCB : to_proto_struct(inputs)\\n: google::protobuf::Struct\n\nGCB -&gt; Stub : stub_-&gt;Run(\\n  PredictRequest {\\n    model_id,\\n    inputs: Struct\\n  }\\n) : PredictResponse\nactivate Stub\n\n== gRPC boundary ==\n\nStub -&gt; WSI : Predict(\\n  ServerContext*,\\n  PredictRequest*,\\n  PredictResponse*\\n) : grpc::Status\nactivate WSI\n\nnote right of WSI\n  **value_convert.hpp**\n  from_proto_struct(request-&gt;inputs())\n  Struct → client::Object\nend note\n\nWSI -&gt; WSI : from_proto_struct(\\n  request-&gt;inputs()\\n) : client::Object\n\nWSI -&gt; IE : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate IE\n\nIE -&gt; IE : check_auto_unload()\n\nnote right of IE\n  Lock mutex_\n  Lookup models_[model_id]\n  → LoadedModel::backend*\n  Unlock mutex_\nend note\n\nIE -&gt; OB : predict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate OB\n\nloop para cada input tensor\n    OB -&gt; OB : value_to_floats(\\n  inputs[name] : Value\\n) : vector&lt;float&gt;\n    OB -&gt; OB : resolve_dynamic_shape(\\n  input_shapes_[i],\\n  data.size(),\\n  name\\n) : vector&lt;int64_t&gt;\n    OB -&gt; OB : Ort::Value::CreateTensor&lt;float&gt;(\\n  mem_info,\\n  data.ptr,\\n  shape\\n)\nend\n\nOB -&gt; OB : session_-&gt;Run(\\n  RunOptions,\\n  input_name_ptrs[],\\n  input_tensors[],\\n  output_name_ptrs[]\\n) : vector&lt;Ort::Value&gt;\n\nloop para cada output tensor\n    OB -&gt; OB : floats_to_value(\\n  ptr : float*,\\n  count : size_t\\n) : client::Value\nend\n\nOB -&gt; OB : metrics_.record(\\n  time_ms, success=true)\nOB -&gt; OB : touch()\n\nOB --&gt; IE : InferenceResult {\\n  success: bool,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double\\n}\ndeactivate OB\n\nIE --&gt; WSI : InferenceResult\ndeactivate IE\n\nnote right of WSI\n  **value_convert.hpp**\n  to_proto_struct(result.outputs)\n  client::Object → Struct\nend note\n\nWSI -&gt; WSI : to_proto_struct(\\n  result.outputs\\n) : google::protobuf::Struct\n\nWSI -&gt; WSI : response-&gt;set_success(true)\\nresponse-&gt;set_inference_time_ms(...)\\n*response-&gt;mutable_outputs() = Struct\n\nWSI --&gt; Stub : grpc::Status::OK\\n+ PredictResponse {\\n    success: true,\\n    outputs: Struct,\\n    inference_time_ms\\n  }\ndeactivate WSI\n\n== gRPC boundary ==\n\nStub --&gt; GCB : PredictResponse\ndeactivate Stub\n\nnote right of GCB\n  **value_convert.hpp**\n  from_proto_struct(resp.outputs())\n  Struct → client::Object\nend note\n\nGCB -&gt; GCB : from_proto_struct(\\n  resp.outputs()\\n) : client::Object\n\nGCB --&gt; IC : PredictionResult {\\n  success: true,\\n  outputs: Object,\\n  inference_time_ms\\n}\ndeactivate GCB\n\nIC --&gt; Caller : PredictionResult\ndeactivate IC\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="OFugE89OlIWmUVSY5UGE-2">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2429" width="1515" x="-1970" y="5260" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
